# libghostty-vt prebuilt — the macOS-arm64 .a is tracked so CI
# can link (8MB; small enough not to need git-lfs). dylibs stay
# ignored because they're only for local dev / dynamic linking
# experiments. Regenerate the .a via vendor/libghostty-vt/README.md.
/vendor/libghostty-vt/lib/*.dylib
